author: Dewayne Bevil
title: Halloween Spooktacular begins again at SeaWorld Orlando
text:
Halloween Spooktacular begins again at SeaWorld Orlando SeaWorld's Halloween Spooktacular SeaWorld's Halloween Spooktacular includes encounters with underseas-themed characters. SeaWorld's Halloween Spooktacular includes encounters with underseas-themed characters. (SeaWorld Orlando) Dewayne Bevil Contact Reporter Orlando Sentinel SeaWorld revs up its Spooktacular event 
WHAT: SeaWorld kicks off its annual Halloween Spooktacular this weekend with trick-or-treating, costumed characters, the bubble-happy Penelope's Party Zone and "Sesame Street's Countdown to Halloween" stage show at Seaport Theater. The park encourages guests to attend in costumes. 
WHEN: Noon-7 p.m., Saturdays and Sundays in October. 
WHERE: Off BeachLine Expressway, southwest of Orlando. 
COST: Spooktacular is Included in regular SeaWorld admission. A one-day ticket is $97 ($92 for ages 3-9). 
CALL: 407-351-3600
